biography: "Women, with their intuitive instinct, understood that I dreamed not only of making them more beautiful, but happier too." Christian Dior

latestIgtvVideos.caption: The #DiorSS24 collection by @MariaGraziaChiuri channels the rebellious and unconventional women in history, its dark undercurrent expressed primarily in black, brightened with lighter hues. Innovatively textured materials reference passing time, incorporating iconography of the French capital, mixing nature with esoterica. Providing the show backdrop, ‘NOT HER’, a monumental digital artwork by @Ele.Bellantoni_Studio, takes on misogynistic advertising.

Inspired by Joséphine Baker, the provocative and progressive African-American performer, muse, activist and Dior client, who dazzled Paris in the 1920s, #DiorCouture Spring-Summer 2023 by @MariaGraziaChiuri is a paean to the power of femininity. From the intimacy of more personal pieces to tailored daywear and glittering gowns to light up the night, the collection unfolds in a symphony of savoir-faire.
© All scenographic artworks by @MickaleneThomas, with embroidery by @Chanakya.In and @Chanakya.School

Regeneration and rejuvenation are at the core of #DiorWinter23 by @MrKimJones, a collection that examines Yves Saint Laurent's brief tenure at the House, exploring transformative volumes, and fusing technology and tradition in an evolution of savoir-faire.
© Music: @MaxRichterMusic

This Holiday season, embark on a festive journey under the Dior Beauty constellations.
An enchanted dinner hosted by @AnyaTaylorJoy at Le Château de La Colle Noire, Christian Dior’s personal floral retreat in South of France. A place filled with memories where the Dior hospitality and generosity is shown to its full extent.

#DiorBeauty #DiorHoliday #DreamInDior

Discover #DiorSS23 by @MariaGraziaChiuri, an enigmatic exploration of the city of Paris and the women who shaped it. The influence of the (in)famous historical figure of Catherine de’ Medici casts a long shadow across the collection, with a prevalence of black in Renaissance silhouettes made over in a contemporary manner, some with sportswear accents. Archival floral and map motifs forge a link with the House’s own identity, as does the sensational savoir-faire contained in magical transformations of raffia and the lavish use of lace and embroideries. The show scenography features a fantastical Baroque grotto by the artist Eva Jospin, realized entirely out of cardboard.
© Choreography by Imre and Marne van Opstal

Colored with references from the dusky pink of Texan sunsets to Monsieur Dior’s gardens and Californian beach culture, #CactusJackDior is a Paris-tinged ode to Americana. A youthful, upbeat capsule, it reanimates a vintage House logo, the #CDDiamond, and reimagines the #DiorOblique pattern to spell ‘Jack’. The sportswear aesthetic mixes bold iconography with a strong tailoring game that balances snug with fluid and flared, and reinvents icons such as the #DiorSaddle bag while introducing ‘B713’ sneakers.
© Video: @Albert__Moya
Photo: @RafaelPavarotti_
Music: Travis Scott

Dior makeup opens a new era, with the first transfer-proof lipstick. Coming soon…

Photographer: @vivianesassenstudio @peterphilipsmakeup 
•
#DiorBeauty #DiorMakeup #ForeverRouge

Delve into the #DiorSavoirFaire behind the ‘DiorCamp’ bag, reinvented by @MariaGraziaChiuri for the #DiorAW22 collection. From the macrocannage’s fluffy silky touch and a luminous finish, to the 'CD' clasp in ruthenium-finish metal, the model is both sleek yet functional in its design. Notice the meticulous techniques implemented by hand that treat even the smallest details like the inner zipper with the utmost finesse. 
© @PolBaril

Immerse yourself in the mood of #DiorAW22 by @MariaGraziaChiuri, a collection suspended between the present and the future, in tune with the time and - featuring the collaborative involvement of @DAirLabOfficial - exploring the fertile overlap between fashion and technology. 
© @BrigitteNiedermair

With its swishing and jewel-encrusted rotor evoking the most extravagant of evening dresses, witness some of the #DiorSavoirFaire of the unique Dior Grand Bal de Printemps watch. This outstanding #DiorHauteHorlogerie timepiece features a rose gold guilloché dial over which the aforementioned, pleat-effect yellow gold rotor swings rhythmically, powered by a 'Dior Inversé 11 ½' automatic movement. At the back of the white gold, snow-set diamond case, a sketch for a ball gown by Monsieur Dior has been recreated as a miniature engraving.
© @PolBaril

Experience the #DiorHauteHorlogerie Dior Grand Soir Libellule watch. An extraordinary feat of #DiorSavoirFaire, and in a limited edition of 18, the precision and precious production combines yellow gold, sapphires, emeralds and amethyst with mother-of-pearl and featherwork for the central dragonfly, which rises from a snow-set diamond dial framed by a pavé bezel. The back of the white gold case is engraved with a depiction of the delicate winged insect from which the timepiece takes its name.
© @PolBaril

The 24h wear Dior Forever Skin Glow foundation features a formula composed of an 86% floral skincare base to intensely hydrate the skin, let it breathe and lastingly improve skin quality.
•
DIOR FOREVER SKIN GLOW

The #DiorMenFall 2025 collection by @KimJonesStudio draws inspiration from the late 1970s and early 1980s. Channeling the vibrant urban feel of New York and Paris, a relaxed yet elegant aesthetic offers a wardrobe of understated luxury, easily styled with the Dior Daily backpack, a reliable companion, or the Bobby zipped mini bag for a whimsical touch. 
© @AlasdairMcLellan

The new #LadyDior handbags come to life in the atelier–a cherished leather form coaxed into being through time-honored #DiorSavoirFaire, guided by @MariaGraziaChiuri’s dreams for #DiorFall25. Watch as each motif unfurls and the magic of craftsmanship takes hold.
© Video: Melinda Triana
Photo: @AndreaCenetiempo

New blooms in the House’s garden of icons: for #DiorFall25, @MariaGraziaChiuri reimagines the #LadyDior with embroidered cherry blossoms and peonies in sculpted relief. Rooted in the philosophy of ikebana, each petal and charm reflects the poetic balance of Japanese decorative art, shaped through #DiorSavoirFaire.
© Sophie Carre & @AndreaCenetiempo

A renewed expression of a House essential, the new #DiorToujours for #DiorFall25 by @MariaGraziaChiuri emerges like a summer day made tangible through #DiorSavoirFaire – its sun-warmed raffia surface woven in cannage, traced with brown leather, and finished with a matching pouch that slips seamlessly inside.
© Video: Melinda Triana
Photo: @AndreaCenetiempo

The #DiorFall25 campaign closes with a luxurious showcase of @MariaGraziaChiuri’s wrap blouses, languid trousers, bermudas, and dresses. Classic palettes hold their intensity while florals carry narrative weight with the #DiorToujours and #DiorCaro accompanying the finish.
© @HirokoMatsubaraa

The glow begins with skin. Dior Eye Patches, Dior Capture Le Sérum and Dior Forever Skin Perfect laid the foundation for a smooth, radiant complexion. With a touch of sparkle on the eyes, a trace of brown along the lashes, and a veil of Dior Forever Glow Luminizer in 06 Opal Sequin on cheeckbones, the look was sculpted with light, then sealed with a soft sheen of Dior Backstage Lip Glow Butter in 103 Toffee. 

#DiorBeauty #DiorMakeup #DiorCruise
